        <item xml:lang="zh">工藝</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SKILL IMPORTANT FOR a PROFESSION.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general word for any craft or professional skill is shù 術. See also METHOD</p>
<p>2. Gōng 工 is the general term for handicrafts.</p>
<p>3. Jì 技 is a general term for highly developed skills of any kind, including the professional skills. See SKILL</p>
        </div>
